# Accessibility

Target practical **WCAG 2.2 AA** on: browse ‚Üí PDP ‚Üí cart ‚Üí checkout ‚Üí account (plus admin money/publish paths).

## Must

| Requirement | How |
|---|---|
| Focus visible | Theme ring tokens ‚Äî never `outline: none` without a replacement |
| Keyboard | Dialogs, menus, cart drawer, builder steps fully operable |
| Icon-only | `aria-label` (password Eye toggle pattern) or visible text |
| Touch | ‚â• 48px targets; primary CTAs often 56px |
| Status | Not by color alone (text / icon / `aria`) |
| Forms | `aria-invalid` + `aria-describedby` tied to error text |
| Images | Product `alt` = name + trait; decorative `alt=""` |
| Motion | Honor `prefers-reduced-motion` ‚Äî price/CTA never trapped at opacity 0 |
| Modals | Focus trap + Escape + restore focus ‚Äî prefer Radix/shadcn |

## Soft Gift contrast

Pink CTAs need white/`--primary-foreground` text. Pastel chips (must/rec/nice): **dark text on pastel fills**, not light-on-light.

